---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for Dev Error DB, including log data, future analytics, future advertising, cookies, and contact information."
>
  <section class="content-page">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>
      Dev Error DB is a static developer troubleshooting website. This Privacy
      Policy explains the basic information that may be collected when you visit
      the site.
    </p>

    <h2>Information We May Collect</h2>
    <p>
      The site or its hosting and CDN providers may collect standard server and
      log data, such as IP address, browser type, requested URL, referring page,
      device information, and request time. This information is commonly used to
      operate, secure, debug, and improve websites.
    </p>

    <h2>Analytics And Advertising</h2>
    <p>
      Dev Error DB may use analytics in the future to understand site traffic
      and page performance. The site may also display ads in the future. If
      analytics or advertising services are added, third-party services may use
      cookies or similar technologies to measure usage, prevent abuse, or serve
      relevant ads.
    </p>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      Third-party services may use cookies or similar technologies if analytics,
      advertising, or other embedded services are enabled. You can control or
      block cookies through your browser settings.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      For privacy questions, contact
      <a href="mailto:contact@dev-error-db.com">contact@dev-error-db.com</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
